     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    C2SMOD
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    W2LOT#
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    W2PAG#
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    W2SMOD
     C                     MOVEL'20'      @@ID
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDSL
     C*
     C                     ENDDO
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
     C**************************************************************************
** CMD
CLRPFM QTEMP/ALCWP30
** ERR   +.........+.........+.........+.........+.........+.........> (70)
ENTER DATE !                                                            01
DATE ERROR !                                                            02
FROM DATE > TODAY !                                                     03
NO DATA FOUND !                                                         04
DATA OVER LIMIT! CHANGE SELECT CONDITION THEN TRY AGAIN.                05
PAGE# VALID WITH LOT#. XXXXX                                            06
SECTION MUST BE CV,OQ,HR OR BLANK=ALL !                                 07
ENTER LOT# !                                                            08
OVER LIMIT (10,000 RECORDS) ! PLEASE CHANGE SELECTION...                09
TIME MUST BE LESS THAN 24:00 !                                          10
